title: noatikl 1.5 for mac
description:
This the latest release of intermorphic&#039;s noatikl for mac. in their own words:

Noatikl is a powerful, easy to use generative music tool that helps you generate new musical ideas.

It uses techniques developed over the last 17 years through our work on the award-winning Koan generative music system, techniques now used in the all-new and superior "Noatikl". 

See http://www.intermorphic.com/tools/noatikl/index.html for more info.
